                                              Alexandra Grömling and Tilman Lingesleben, <em>Alessandro Botticelli, 1444/45-1510</em>, Könemann Verlagsgesellschaft (Köln, Germany, 1998), pp. 98-101, fig. 110, repr. in color on p. 100
