                                              Francesca Bewer, <em>A Laboratory for Art: Harvard's Fogg Museum and the Emergence of Conservation in America, 1900-1950</em>, Harvard Art Museum and Yale University Press (U.S.) (Cambridge, MA, 2010), p. 106-107, fig. 3.15
